{"tid":1116646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎棟國：逃犯條例不設追溯期並不可行","createTime":"2019-04-20T06:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T07:15:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10e3e6622a803d832b90cae35af2de9fb5cf4525","tid":1116646,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/CR-CRIME-190420-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FCR-CRIME-190420-11.jpg&h=65a5c842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】逃犯條例首次法案委員會會議未能選出正副主席。前保安局局長兼立法會議員葉劉淑儀認為，即使未能趕及處理台灣殺人案的疑犯，亦應盡力完成修訂。另一名前保安局局長黎棟國重申，條例是根據國際水平制定，不設追溯期並不可行。<br />\n<br />\n香港島立法會議員葉劉淑儀：「這個問題已懸而未決廿多年，因張子強案無法將在內地逮捕的嫌疑人移交香港，立法會很強烈的意見敦促我與中央商討方案。他們都明白是雙向的，你要別人移交給你，你也要移交給人。這次既然政府找到方法用個案形式處理，就算不能解決潘家的問題，都應該完成這個修訂。」<br />\n<br />\n前保安局局長黎棟國：「一個人以前犯了法，被當地執法機關通緝，這一定是過去式的，沒有現在式或將來式。假如不能追溯，即整條條例對所有修訂前的事情都廢了，逃犯條例針對的都是過去式，這與立法原意相違背。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=345136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345136&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLLBzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=23c310c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345136&h=846481bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=345136</a>"},{"pid":"1a1b768aa212d4370e6653d62955d1718478ad0c","tid":1116646,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"大劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bc736ec6be61d0c12142a3d611771335557567","tid":1116646,"uid":112583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1a1b768aa212d4370e6653d62955d1718478ad0c","tid":1116646,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"大劉<img src=\"